đang lâm nguy.


156
00:13:07.450 --> 00:13:08.993
Vậy "chúng tôi" là ai?

157
00:13:10.536 --> 00:13:11.955
Chào, Tony.

158
00:13:11.955 --> 00:13:13.081
Bruce.

159
00:13:13.081 --> 00:13:14.582
